                    <button class="btn btn-primary" id="detailed-btn">DETAILED RESULT</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="right-panel">
                <div class="guide-section">
                    <h2>Guide</h2>
                    <div class="guide-content">
                        <p>Drag the START(üòä) and TARGET(üè†) icons to change their positions, and click on the blank nodes to add Walls.</p>
                        
                        <div class="legend">
